  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "2001-06-21", 
    "text": "Amends the Internal Revenue Code with respect to environmental remediation cost expensing to: (1) make such provision permanent; (2) include toxic substances within the definition of \"hazardous substance\"; (3) include toxic substances or structures containing hazardous or toxic substances within the definition of \"qualified contaminated site\"; and (4) eliminate a related recapture provision."
